text: Franco Martín Muñoz Rodríguez (born 6 February 1999) is a Uruguayan footballer who plays as a midfielder for Juventud de Las Piedras in the Uruguayan Primera División. ==References== Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Juventud de Las Piedras players Category:Uruguayan Primera División players Category:Uruguayan Segunda División players Category:Uruguayan footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:People from Santa Lucía, Uruguay
